column5: Hi all,  Had a couple of relaxed sessions for a couple hours a piece last week.  One trip with member Havtaflyfish and one with Havtaflyfish and my buddy Cliff.  First off..... the events with Havtaflyfishnd myself   PIKE ARE NUTS!  <iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/mLE5J8e9ZZw" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>      next day after work it was onto another local pond...      A PEACEFULL EVENING TOO  <iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/ctH7CYMaRG4" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>    warm up sessions!
Love watching pike take a fish that's being reeled in. Swallowed that walleye in no time at all.
awesome couple hours that pike ate that little eye big time
